== 环境准备

.Ubuntu
[soruce, bash]
----
sudo apt install gem
gem install bundle
bundle config set path 'vendor/bundle'
bundle install
----

.Archlinux
[soruce, bash]
----
sudo pacman -S graphviz
sudo pacman install gem
gem install bundle
bundle config set path 'vendor/bundle'
bundle install
----

== 生成文档

.生成html格式
[souce, bash]
